	   <tr><td colspan=2>I played this game for a long time, well, not that long, I was a 19th level dwarven warrior.<br>I began to find it increasingly difficult to find a desent, and dependable group that actually knew what they were doing.I found myself dying alot.<br>I tried soloing, but to little or no avail.<br>Is it possible to solo as a warrior?<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
